ZH: 我在镜子里看见了自己的倒影。
EN: I saw my reflection in the mirror.

ZH: 这个镜子太脏了，我看不清楚自己。
EN: The mirror is too dirty, I can't see myself clearly.

ZH: 她每天都要花很长时间照镜子。
EN: She spends a lot of time looking at herself in the mirror every day.

ZH: 镜子里的光线很明亮。
EN: The light in the mirror is very bright.

ZH: 这面镜子有点破。
EN: This mirror is a little bit broken.

ZH: 我能看到后面的东西，因为镜子倾斜了。
EN: I can see things behind me because the mirror is tilted.

ZH: 镜子反射了阳光。
EN: The mirror reflected the sunlight.

ZH: 我不喜欢看镜子里的自己。
EN: I don't like seeing myself in the mirror.

ZH: 镜子上有很多污渍。
EN: There are a lot of stains on the mirror.

ZH: 镜子里有条裂缝。
EN: There is a crack in the mirror.

ZH: 灰尘遮住了镜子。
EN: Dust has covered the mirror.

ZH: 她整天都在看着镜子。
EN: She is constantly looking at herself in the mirror.

ZH: 镜子的边缘摔碎了。
EN: The edge of the mirror is shattered.

ZH: 镜子反射了整个房间的景象。
EN: The mirror reflected the entire room.

ZH: 镜子反射了我心中的渴望。
EN: The mirror reflected my inner desires.

ZH: 镜子里看不到她的笑容。
EN: I can't see her smile in the mirror.

ZH: 镜子里的景象异常清晰。
EN: The image in the mirror is exceptionally clear.

ZH: 镜子反射出来的画面非常美丽。
EN: The reflection in the mirror is very beautiful.

ZH: 镜子反射的光线形成了一个光环。
EN: The light reflected by the mirror formed a halo.

ZH: 镜子里的我和现实中的我不一样。
EN: The me in the mirror is different from the me in reality.
